                },
                {
                    "header": "Part 3",
                    "description": "Wait by the rocket until test launch starts. After the test starts, interact with the lever under the rocket. Then wait behind the blast doors until the test is over, and a control panel will light up. Interact with the panel, then pick up the part inside the teleporter.",
                    "elements": [
                        {
                            "pic": {
                                "src": "/local/935/de/19.png",
